OL,3,CGrandma finally allowed to visit
OL,4,Cgrandchildren in UK after visa row
OL,6,FA grandmother has finally made the
OL,7,F5,000 mile journey to see her triplet
OL,8,Fgrandsons - after a 12 month visa
OL,9,Fbattle.
OL,11,FGurmeet Kaur, who lives in India, was
OL,12,Fblocked from seeing the newborns after
OL,13,Fher visa application was turned down
OL,14,Ffive times.
OL,16,FBut after featuring on Granada Reports
OL,17,Fin September 2023, a solicitor stepped
OL,18,Finto help the grandmother, and she has
OL,19,Ffinally made the journey to Hale, in
OL,20,FGreater Manchester.
