OL,3,CGrandma finally allowed to visit
OL,4,Cgrandchildren in UK after visa row
OL,6,FMaddy said it has been a long road to
OL,7,Fsort out the visa.
OL,9,F"Talk about red tape," she said, "it
OL,10,Fhas just been one thing after another.
OL,12,F"You think you get everything in place
OL,13,Fwith finances and you prove you can
OL,14,Fhouse her and look after her, you
OL,15,Fapply and apply and apply and then
OL,16,Fdevelop a bit of resilience because
OL,17,Fit's a relentless process."
OL,19,FThe family are now thrilled to have
OL,20,FMrs Kaur stay and see her bonding with
OL,21,Fher grandsons.
